The two walked over to Spears'.

"Ye like her? We named ker the Iron Ram, after Iron Raptor and 
Rmulus, two people who helped us alot. We're gonna go finish up our 
work on the CR Chambers. If you could make up the list of the parts 
we need, we might be able to go as soon as tomorrow. Thanks!"

Brix and Fliq walk off into The Ark
